README
======

gjiten-2.7

A modified version of the original gjiten-2.6, based on the Debian package "gjiten".

Copyright (C) 2013 by Jens Oliver John <dev@2ion.de>
Licensed under the GNU General Public License v3 or later.

gjiten 2.6 is Copyright (C) 1999-2005 by Botond Botyanski
<boti@rocketmail.com> and licensed under the GNU General Public License v2.

See the original README (./README.original).

AMD64 builds are hosted on Bitbucket: <https://bitbucket.org/2ion/gjiten/downloads>.

Note that in current Sid, this package has a FTBS bug which is fixed in
the current Debian package. Before building again, you should import the
/debian folder from there.

CHANGES since 2.6
=================

    * Remove superfluous toolbar icons
    * Fix broken GTK stock icon associations in the toolbar
